00:03:34.291 --> 00:03:35.875
We will have to look at

00:03:35.875 --> 00:03:38.750
the ultraviolet radiation coming from the star

00:03:38.750 --> 00:03:40.750
to see if life can survive.

00:03:40.750 --> 00:03:43.750
So once we put all these pieces together,

00:03:43.750 --> 00:03:46.083
I do believe that we will find life somewhere.

00:03:46.083 --> 00:03:48.208
It's not going to be easy,

00:03:48.208 --> 00:03:49.709
